README for uPortal Documents directory

In this directory you'll find documentation for JA-SIG's uPortal
framework. The documentation is in a few different formats, and you
can compile them into a few other formats as explained in the sections
below.

Manifest
--------

README                    this file
buildPortalJavaDocs.bat   a MS-DOS batch file wrapper for creating 
                           javadocs on windows. 
TODO                      planned features not yet implemented
BUGS                      known problems
VERSION                   the current version number
WhatsNew                  changes since the last public release
                           for a complete list of changes, see the ChangeLog
                           file(s))
javadocs/                 HTML documentation produced by the javadoc tool. 
diagrams/                 UML diagrams describing uPortal internals
overview.html             HTMl installation guide for the uPortal framework
overview.xml              XML source for overview.html
uPortalDoc.xsl            XSL stylesheet for producing overview.html

Changes
-------

See the ChangeLog for additional information about the specific changes.

See WhatsNew for changes since the last release.


Formats
